   <p><note place="header">322</note>
<lb/><date when="1863-11-19">Nov<hi rend="sup">r.</hi> 19<hi rend="underline">"</hi> <gap/>3.</date>
<lb/>Gen<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">l</hi></hi> L. Thomas
<lb/>Adjutant Gen<hi rend="sup">l</hi> U. S.
<lb/>Washington
<lb/>Sir,</p>
<p>I am instructed by the Governor to request the discharge of 3<hi rend="sup">rd</hi> Serg<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">t</hi></hi> Gaines L. Burk. Co<hi rend="sup">y</hi> H. 12 Ky. Inf<hi rend="sup">y.</hi> to accept promotion as 1<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">s</hi></hi> Lieut 30 Ky Infantry. His command is recruited and in the field.</p>
<p>Resp<hi rend="sup">y</hi>
<lb/>Your obd<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">t</hi></hi> Servant
<lb/><hi rend="underline">John Boyle</hi>
<lb/>Adj<hi rend="sup">t</hi> Gen<hi rend="sup">l</hi> of Ky</p>
